        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 15. (a, b, f–i) Ulskia schorygini (Logvinenko & Starobogatov, 1969): (a, b) Holotype (ZIN 4357/1); (f, g) Paratype (ZIN 9); (h, i) Paratype (ZIN 9). (c, d) U. cf. schorygini, specimen labelled as “Caspia turrita, paratype 2” (ZIN, no number). (e, j). Caspiella? sp., specimen labelled as “Caspia turrita, holotype” (ZIN, no number). All material from the South Caspian Basin off Apsheron Peninsula (locality 15). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4550188/files/figure.png" .

