        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 16. Ulskia ulskii (Clessin & Dybowski in Dybowski, 1887) from the Caspian Sea Basin. (a) Lectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 76). (b) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 78). (c) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 78). (d) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 76). (e) Paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 76). (f, k) Specimen from locality 17 (ZIN, no number). (g, h) Holotype of Pyrgula nana, locality 15 (ZIN, no number). (i, j) Specimen labelled as “Caspia clessiniolaeformis, holotype”, locality 17 (ZIN, no number). (l) Holotype of Pyrgula behningi, locality 23 (ZIN 1). (m) Paratype of P. behningi, locality 14 (ZIN 2). (n, o) Paratype of P. behningi, locality 14 (ZIN 2). (p–s, u) Five specimens from the Holocene of the Kura delta (localities 25d and 25f, RGM 1310306–1310310). (t, v–z) Three specimens from Selitrennoye (locality 1, RGM 1309810, 1309809, 1309856). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4550190/files/figure.png" .

